author: Geri B.
description: You want the best food in London go to Ffionas. The owner is wonderful and runs the restaurant on the floor. The food is to die for. Especially the Toffee Pudding, holy moly!!! Like last meal type good. A lot of locals come and it's a real home type feel. Catch the music on the ceilings it's pretty awesome. Don't miss this delicious meal in London, I promise you won't regret it.
